hidden_gems_uniform_exploration.title: Something Completely Different
hidden_gems_uniform_exploration.description: We picked these out just for you.

289890.title: Super Hybrid
289890.description: Nothing seems amiss when the Chicago police impound a car after an accident — until the car turns out to be a killing machine able to outsmart anyone.

300459.title: Not Without My Daughter
300459.description: In this thriller based on a true story, an Iranian-American man takes his American wife and daughter to visit Iran, only to keep them hostage there.

300461.title: Quigley Down Under
300461.description: A man hired as a sharpshooter travels to Australia, where he learns his new, high-paying job has a morbid catch that leaves him conflicted.

300846.title: The Wraith
300846.description: A mysterious black turbo racing car appears and challenges a murderous gang leader to a series of races. The driver's identity may surprise everyone.

302493.title: Shaquille O'Neal Presents: All Star Comedy Jam - South Beach
302493.description: The all-star comedy line-up includes host D.L. Hughley and featured comics Earthquake, Lavell Crawford, Melanie Comarcho, and Arnez J.

302505.title: The Substitute
302505.description: Undercover as a substitute teacher, an ex-marine cleans up the crime-infested school when he discovers a gang tormenting students and staff.

302753.title: Yours, Mine And Ours
302753.description: A hilarious true story of a widow and widower whose marriage creates a full house of twenty as they blend their families.

304779.title: Joshua
304779.description: A possible second coming of Christ shakes up the rural town of Auburn in the form of a kind carpenter who seems capable of performing miracles.

307480.title: The Gallant Hours
307480.description: Based on true events, an American commander in the South Pacific during World War II makes a critical move that helps them defeat the Japanese forces.

312179.title: Get Shorty
312179.description: A gangster goes to Hollywood to collect a debt and becomes a big-time producer when he realizes the movie business runs a lot like the mob.

316468.title: Larry the Cable Guy: Health Inspector
316468.description: A bumbling big city health inspector is paired with a no-nonsense rookie partner to investigate a series of fine dining food poisoning incidents.

389496.title: What's the Worst That Could Happen?
389496.description: A professional thief tries to rob a billionaire's mansion. But when the crook’s lucky ring is stolen, he vows revenge in this laugh-out-loud comedy.

437418.title: Boarding Gate
437418.description: From Olivier Assayas comes an erotic thriller about a former prostitute and her onetime pimp-turned-high powered businessman at the center of it.

445669.title: Death of a Cheerleader
445669.description: An investigation into the stabbing of a popular and beautiful cheerleader.

456403.title: Woman Thou Art Loosed
456403.description: A life of dysfunction and abuse entagles a woman in the world of drugs, prostitution and imprisonment, but her healing begins behind bars.

456923.title: The Iceman
456923.description: Based on a shocking true story, a family man goes to great lengths to keep his work as a ruthless hitman a secret from the people he loves.

460204.title: King of New York
460204.description: A New York drug lord just released from prison is determined to rule the streets again with a vengeance in this gritty action film.

461203.title: Instructions Not Included
461203.description: An Acapulco playboy's life turns upside down when a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep, and he has to raise the child on his own.

463206.title: El Pistolero
463206.description: Un poderoso llega a un pueblo en busca de nuevos pistoleros para su equipo y un hombre sencillo acepta el trabajo para vengar la muerte de su padre.

470760.title: Pride and Glory
470760.description: A New York homicide detective is assigned to investigate the precinct run by his brother and where his best friend is also a suspected corrupt cop.

472710.title: Lionheart
472710.description: After the murder of his brother, a tough soldier goes AWOL and enters the underground world of bare-knuckle fighting to support his family.

475190.title: Apartment 407
475190.description: Based on true events, a single mother goes to a photo studio for a modeling shoot but gets drugged and sold into sex slavery as she fights to escape.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

480226.title: Gacy
480226.description: He appeared to be a model citizen, father, and husband. This film dives into the psyche of this serial killer, who murdered over thirty men and boys.

491388.title: Friends for Life
491388.description: A retired attorney, whose wife’s death left his family shattered, raises four orphaned wolf pups to adulthood - who later pay him back warmly.

496421.title: Dangerous Intentions
496421.description: A battered woman has no allies in her family or the legal system. The danger of escape is vivid after her friend is killed by her own abusive husband.

497277.title: Gracie's Choice
497277.description: When her drug-addicted, alcoholic, abusive mother is sent to jail, a teenage girl fights to be legally emancipated and raise her siblings on her own.

498170.title: Child Bride of Short Creek
498170.description: Based on the lives of members of a fanatical cult of Mormon separatists, children suffer damage from the practices of child marriage and polygamy.

514459.title: The Mighty Macs
514459.description: Based on a true story, coach Cathy Rush joins a women's Catholic college basketball team and fights to help it succeed against the starkest odds.

521163.title: Identity Theft
521163.description: The true story of Michelle Brown, who accrues over $50,000 of debt after her identity is stolen, traces her journey and how she helps change laws.

526131.title: The Life of Jesus
526131.description: The life of Jesus is recounted from the perspective of one of his apostles, according to the Gospel of John,  and narrated by Christopher Plummer.

543987.title: Parker
543987.description: Based on the Donald E. Westlake novels, a thief works by a code of integrity and makes it his mission to avenge all that cross him or work dirty.

551867.title: Something in the Woods
551867.description: Inspired by true events of the 1960s, the story follows a family and their dealings with what might be Sasquatch, near their remote farmhouse.

552333.title: Daddy Day Camp
552333.description: Two dads apply their childcare magic to an underdog day camp and discover that teamwork, with a dash of craziness, makes for an unforgettable summer.

557519.title: After Earth
557519.description: Following a crash landing on Earth, a young boy and his estranged father must make an arduous journey and survive the elements to signal for help.

557537.title: 16 and Missing
557537.description: An FBI agent must save her 16-year-old daughter after she runs away to meet an older man she met online.

561851.title: 2Eleven
561851.description: Two brothers and fellow hustlers with very different motivations for committing robberies come to blows the more their criminal enterprise grows.

562905.title: Buffed Up
562905.description: Believing that all it takes to score with the ladies is a pair of Cartier frames, three college students hustle for the money, no matter the cost.

565093.title: Baggage Claim
565093.description: Paula Patton stars as flight attendant Montana Moore, who is tired of the single life, hoping to meet the perfect man before her sister’s wedding.

569452.title: Kevin Hart: Laugh at My Pain
569452.description: The hilarious comic keeps it real by showing his Philadelphia roots, where he first started honing the skills that would make him a comedy superstar.

571897.title: Wolf Town
571897.description: A group of friends on a weekend trip find themselves trapped by a pack of ferocious wolves and must fight to survive as they are hunted down.

576492.title: Highway 395
576492.description: The sheriff of a small community is challenged when he has to contend with drug runners, convicts and a serial killer all at the same time.

580532.title: Lucky Number Slevin
580532.description: A mysterious man is roped into a dangerous feud between two rival crime kingpins, neither of whom can step foot outside for fear of assassination.

581300.title: Diana
581300.description: The bedroom of an apartment in Paseo de la Castellana, Madrid. It is Sofia's bedroom, a deluxe escort. Her new client discovers the name that is tattoed on her leg 'Diana'... Is it your real name?' He introduced himself as Hugo, but his real name is Jano. Who is really Sofia? According to an interview aired on an investigative tv program, 'a social waste, a victim who didn't know how to survive the economic crisis'. Who is Jano? Society portrays him as a symbol of the entrepreneur of the future, an example to follow. Sofia's apartment becomes the stage where the personality or personalities of both will be revealed as onion layers until reaching the core. And the key to Sofia's is to discover who is Diana and what does she mean to her...

581680.title: House of Secrets
581680.description: Just as Julie is starting over after her divorce and moves into the house her ex was building for them, someone begins breaking in to spy on her.

589111.title: The Lost Boys
589111.description: Sleep all day. Party all night. Never grow old. Never die. When a woman and her sons move to a California town, they discover the fun of vampire life.

592988.title: Ann Rule's Too Late to Say Goodbye
592988.description: Based on the popular crime novel, a wife’s death after finding out her husband cheated on her comes down to either her husband or her online crush.

594095.title: Horrible Bosses
594095.description: The comedy smash about three co-workers who decide, after a lot of liquor, to get rid of their awful bosses and only manage to make things way worse.

602253.title: Jupiter Ascending
602253.description: The visionaries of ‘The Matrix’ films return with the thrilling story of a genetically engineered tracker who informs a woman of her cosmic destiny.

604324.title: The Super
604324.description: When tenants of an apartment begin disappearing, a former cop-turned-building superintendent suspects a sadistic murderer is at the center of it.

608954.title: Above Majestic
608954.description: A sci-fi expose that looks to answer the question of whether a secret space program was withheld from public knowledge and what that means.

609562.title: Lavell Crawford: New Look, Same Funny
609562.description: Comedian and “Breaking Bad” icon Lavell Crawford shows off his new weight loss, new attitude, and explains how to cope with the mean streets.

611638.title: Son of Bigfoot
611638.description: A teen longs to know his father and sets out on the adventure of a lifetime to find out who he is- only to learn that his old man is Bigfoot!

616782.title: Looking in the Mirror
616782.description: In life you have to play the hand you're dealt, and when faced with a lifetime of adversity, Roslyn Jones does just that. Based on a true story.

616832.title: Enhanced
616832.description: In order to stop a mutant serial killer from hunting her down, a young woman with enhanced abilities must face impossible decisions to stop him.

617476.title: The Guardian
617476.description: A jaded Coast Guard trainer butts heads with an arrogant young recruit, as the two prepare for deadly missions and daunting rescues.

621683.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective
621683.description: When the mascot for football’s Miami Dolphins is stolen, a wacky detective goes undercover, underwater, and in over his head, to get his man or beast.

622272.title: Lockdown: 2025
622272.description: When a highly contagious virus puts the entire country on lockdown, enforced by martial law, one family learns they’re not safe in their own home.

625413.title: The Scorpion King: Book of Souls
625413.description: When an evil warlord gains a sword that can steal souls, the Scorpion King and the sister of a Nubian king must find the one thing that can stop him.

625420.title: The Scorpion King 3: Battle for Redemption
625420.description: When the Scorpion King is hired to guard a beleaguered king, things are not as they seem, so it is up to him and a lady assassin to save Scandinavia.

629330.title: Eliminators
629330.description: After a former U.S. federal agent’s home is invaded and his daughter is put in danger, he must leave the witness protection program to save her life.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

637438.title: Infidelity
637438.description: Struggling within a passionless marriage, a woman decides to fulfill her own desires, by breaking away from her husband and the woman she once was.

643938.title: Sor Tequila
643938.description: La India María, que es requetebuena para los deportes, se mete de monja y siempre anda metiendo la pata por querer ayudar a la gente.

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: John Wayne and Maureen O’Hara reunite in this Western about a no-nonsense rancher who hunts down the outlaw gang that abducted his grandson.

647529.title: These Men for Everybody
647529.description: They say you should keep your friends close and your enemies even closer. But sometimes it’s hard to tell them apart.

652212.title: All-American Girl: The Mary Kay Letourneau
652212.description: "Carlito's Way" star Penelope Ann Miller plays the school teacher who went to jail more than once for seducing a student and having his children.

654968.title: Out of Control
654968.description: Against her father's wishes a young Chicago cop pursues her dream of becoming a detective when she's brought on to investigate a major murder case.

656401.title: True Justice: Lethal Justice
656401.description: With the killer caught the team believe the case is closed, but when another victim appears Sarah unwittingly becomes the target of the real killer.

659798.title: Catch the Bullet
659798.description: A U.S. Marshal sets out to rescue his kidnapped son from a vengeful outlaw and his gang. Both parties face deadly dangers in the desert.

660852.title: The Stalking of Laurie Show
660852.description: When Butch’s girlfriend walks in on him sexually assualting the new girl at school, she blames the victim by framing her as the instigator.

662183.title: Sexo, Amor Y Otras Perversiones
662183.description: Ocho relatos independientes a cargo de prestigiados directores de cine que plasman su visión acerca de las relaciones humanas, el amor y el sexo.

663440.title: Dead Man Down
663440.description: A hitman for a New York crime lord is seduced and blackmailed by a victim seeking retribution who leads him on a violent and cathartic revenge spree.

664874.title: Carrie
664874.description: An adaptation of the classic novel. Carrie, a girl with telekinetic powers, teaches her classmates a deadly lesson when they humiliate her at prom.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

672234.title: Meet the Blacks
672234.description: After Carl Black moves his family to Beverly Hills, their arrival is timed with the city's annual purge, where all crime is legal for 12 hours.

675100.title: Jasper, Texas
675100.description: True account of a black man who accepted a ride from three white men who cuffed him to a truck and dragged him to death.

676860.title: Bone Tomahawk
676860.description: When a group of individuals kidnaps settlers from a small town, an unlikely team of gunslingers, led by Sheriff Hunt, sets out to bring them home.

678633.title: I Am Gangster
678633.description: A rebellious teenager, a hardcore gang member, and an idealistic cop risk everything to find their place in the crumbling fabric of modern America.

680196.title: Dangerous
680196.description: A reformed sociopath travels to a remote island to uncover the truth behind his brother’s mysterious death, but he's met by a band of mercenaries.

681753.title: The Seven Five
681753.description: Meet the dirtiest cop in NYC history. Michael Dowd tells about his years stealing money and dealing drugs while patrolling the streets of Brooklyn.

684103.title: The Lost Tribe
684103.description: Shipwrecked on a remote island, a group of friends discover they are being hunted by a tribe of monstrous, flesh-eating evolutionary throwbacks.

684884.title: Don't Breathe
684884.description: A group of teens breaks into a blind man's home, thinking they'll get away with the perfect crime but get more than they bargained for once inside.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

688929.title: In the Line of Fire
688929.description: The story of a man looking to redeem himself by saving the life of America's highest elected official, even if it means sacrificing himself.

689532.title: Rebound
689532.description: Suspended by the NCAA, a hotheaded basketball coach is forced to reevaluate his life when he's forced to coach a junior high team for a season.

689652.title: In the Heat of the Night
689652.description: While traveling in the deep south, a black Philadelphian homicide detective becomes embroiled in a murder investigation.

691220.title: Alone in the Dark
691220.description: A recent divorcée under house arrest must deal with a stalker that appears to have control over her surroundings.

694227.title: The Rundown
694227.description: A wild action-adventure about a bounty hunter named Beck, who's searching for a rebellious mobster's son and a priceless treasure in the Amazon.

694396.title: It
694396.description: In the town of Derry, Maine, seven young kids band together to stop a new killing cycle of an ancient, shape-shifting predator they can only call It.

696718.title: The Girl Who Believes in Miracles
696718.description: Young Sara discovers her prayers have the power to heal but soon learns the cost may be too high. Can her family save her before it’s too late?

696806.title: A Walk to Remember
696806.description: North Carolina teens Landon Carter and Jamie Sullivan are thrown together after one gets into trouble and is sentenced to community service.

696858.title: No Better Love
696858.description: A love triangle turns deadly when a street savvy hustler finds herself at a crossroads between her drug-dealing boyfriend and a better life.

698967.title: Inmate #1: The Rise of Danny Trejo
698967.description: This captivating documentary film looks into the thoroughly extraordinary life story of Hollywood's most unlikely hero, Danny Trejo.

701398.title: The Minute You Wake Up Dead
701398.description: In this noir thriller, a stockbroker romances a waitress as multiple murders shock a small Southern town. Someone’s getting rich. But who?

702534.title: El Cuatrero
702534.description: Con engaños, Álvaro y Mariana roban una camioneta y un caballo al ranchero Lázaro, quien los busca para recuperar sus pertenencias.

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
702670.description: Un boxeador retirado entra a trabajar en un centro nocturno donde se enamora de una de las bailarinas y tiene que lidiar con varios personajes.

702693.title: El Señor De Las Calles (Doblado)
702693.description: Cuando un entrenador se niega a hacer que su luchador tire una cerilla, un notorio gángster cobra la deuda matando a su luchador y secuestrando a su hija.

702992.title: Vault
702992.description: In this gripping thriller based on true events, two small-time crooks cook up an ill-fated scheme to rip off $30 million belonging to the local mafia.

703676.title: He Played Me 2
703676.description: In this sequel, Yazmin recovers and looks to move on from the aftermath of her tumultuous affair with Jai that threatened her life.

705459.title: Swung
705459.description: A graphic, touching and funny romance that delves into the secret underside of a very modern relationship taken to its emotional and sexual limits.

707321.title: 3 From Hell
707321.description: After barely surviving prison, the demented Firefly clan goes on the run and unleashes a whole new wave of murder, madness and mayhem on the innocent.

707513.title: Big Stan
707513.description: Panicked he’ll be defenseless in prison, a gutless con man sentenced to hard time for fraud gets 11th hour training from a martial arts master.

708341.title: #Float
708341.description: Things turn deadly for Kali and her friends at the annual river float, as a sinister paranormal force plunges them into a life or death struggle.

708829.title: The Stepmother 2
708829.description: Elizabeth breaks free from the hospital with a new mission - find a new family and live happily ever after, she can’t escape her past and will fight.

710214.title: Invasion of the Mermaids
710214.description: When a mysterious water monster invades a fishing community on the South China Sea, it's up to a young man to protect his fiancé and the villagers.

711013.title: Mid90s
711013.description: A 13-year-old spends his summer navigating a troubled home life and skating with a crew of new friends.

712181.title: Street Moves: The Movie
712181.description: A local drug dealer seems to have it all under control until he makes a decision in front of an undercover cop that would cost him everything.

713216.title: El Camino Secreto (Doblado)
713216.description: Una joven blanca abusada por su abuelo encuentra felicidad cuando es tomada bajo el ala de una pareja negra mayor.

713622.title: The Exit Row
713622.description: A chance meeting on a flight between an advertising executive and a real estate mogul leads to a deadly obsession and one woman’s fight for survival.

714235.title: Deadly Secrets
714235.description: When lovers become enemies, friends become foes. A night of fun for a philandering man proves to be a deadly secret in this scandalous drama.

714245.title: Hell in My Life: The Stacey Staxx Story
714245.description: Chasing money and the fast life, a 16-year-old enters the world of sex work after being molested by her mother's boyfriend. Based on true events.

714654.title: Almost Heroes
714654.description: In 1804, a habitually drunk tracker and his foppish blowhard pal lead a crew of misfits on a race to beat Lewis and Clark to the Pacific Ocean.

716834.title: The Three Stooges
716834.description: While trying to save their childhood home, knuckleheads Larry, Curly, and Moe wind up embroiled in a murder plot and stumble into roles on reality TV.

722436.title: It’s Lonely at the Top
722436.description: A gangster-turned-legit professional tries to lead his people in the right direction, only to come to realize they’ve become his worst enemy.

724306.title: Devil's Knot
724306.description: The rural Arkansas town of West Memphis makes national headlines when three teenagers are arrested for the brutal murders of three young boys.

724355.title: The Dirty
724355.description: When Wig kills a young woman, it puts him under investigation by Sergeant Mike Laws, who gets tasked with finding out who committed the murder.

724377.title: Downfall
724377.description: Traudl Junge, the final secretary for Adolf Hitler, tells of the Nazi dictator's final days in his Berlin bunker at the end of World War II.

724735.title: True to the Game 3
724735.description: Gena wakes to find Quadir is her savior and has just 72 hrs to return to Philly to let Bria and Gah Git know her plans, before her happily ever after.

725035.title: The Closest Ones
725035.description: While his marriage falls apart over his wife’s past infidelity, Ryan does the unthinkable by starting an affair with his best friend's fiancée.

725954.title: Always and Forever
725954.description: When Nicole's childhood friends start dying from alleged suicides, she suspects their deaths are linked to a grave mistake they made in middle school.

100000092.title: The Perfect Game
100000092.description: A retiring MLB player heads home to Mexico where he’s recruited by a ragtag team of kids to lead them to the 1957 Little League World Series.

100000215.title: Man of the House
100000215.description: A hard-edged Texas Ranger is forced to go undercover as an assistant coach to protect a group of college cheerleaders after they witness a murder.

100000293.title: Plus One at an Amish Wedding
100000293.description: Doctor April's new romance with handsome veterinarian Jesse seems perfect—until they get invited to a wedding with the Amish family he left behind.

100000334.title: Queen of Cocaine
100000334.description: In a crime world built formen, only onewomanwas daring enough to pave the way for the most infamous Colombian cartels: Griselda Blanco, the Godmother of Cocaine.

100000446.title: Butterscotch Chocolate
100000446.description: Roni is a successful lawyer, but mental illness and sex addiction threaten to throw her career off course with deadly consequences.

100000556.title: No Escape
100000556.description: A soldier convicted for murdering his commanding officer is dumped and left to die on a prison island inhabited by two camps of convicts.

100000587.title: Fireproof
100000587.description: This story follows one man's desire to transform his life and marriage through the healing power of faith and fully embrace the fireman's code.

100000708.title: Equal Standard
100000708.description: After a detective is shot by one of his own NYPD brothers, communities march for justice, and gangs put their differences aside for a united fight.

100000747.title: Dead Hot
100000747.description: After a ghost hunt gone wrong, students of witchcraft Vanessa Hudgens and GG Magree travel to Salem, Massachusetts to seek out proper mentorship from experts in witchcraft.

100000798.title: The Secret She Kept
100000798.description: A successful attorney starts behaving erratically during a political campaign, leading her new husband to suspect she's been hiding a mental illness.

100000844.title: Exam
100000844.description: When eight candidates enter a windowless room to compete for a job at a mysterious and powerful company, the stakes soon become life or death.

100000850.title: Booksmart
100000850.description: About to graduate, two best friends try to cram four years of fun into one night after spending their high school years entirely focused on studying.

100000946.title: Queen of Kings
100000946.description: Tired of the way she is being treated by the drug lords, dancer Alicia decides to rally her girls to take over the Detroit drug game.

100001038.title: The Heavenly Kid
100001038.description: A lonely teen gets divine intervention when a hip guardian angel trying to earn his wings comes down to teach the high schooler how to be cool.

100001040.title: Chedda Boys
100001040.description: After graduating high school, a basketball prospect eager to make his name decides to help his cousins expand the family drug-dealing business.

100001169.title: Why Stop Now?
100001169.description: When a piano prodigy tries to take his mother to rehab, a drug dealer takes them hostage and sweeps them into an adventure they were not expecting.

100001191.title: The Pack
100001191.description: Man's best friend becomes his worst nightmare when a horde of wild dogs descends upon a family's farmhouse in a fang-bearing fight for survival.

100001195.title: Our House
100001195.description: A machine that can bring back dead loved ones seems like a great idea for a young inventor, until he unleashes the wrong spirits in his family home.

100001316.title: Shark Waters
100001316.description: Miles away from shore, a fishing boat is attacked by great white sharks. Those aboard must fight for their lives to avoid being eaten alive.

100001362.title: Student Services
100001362.description: In order to pay for school, a broke French student becomes a massage artist and then resorts to turning tricks. Based on the steamy book by Laura D.

100001390.title: Tale of Tales
100001390.description: This inventive anthology film brings us three gory, gorgeous, grown-up stories of magic, monsters, and royalty based on Italian fairy tales.

100001409.title: The Big Red One
100001409.description: Deemed one of the most powerful films ever made about World War II, this story follows a squad of sharpshooters trying not to die in the Big Red One.

100001476.title: RocketMan
100001476.description: An accident-prone computer programmer’s childhood dream comes true when he’s selected by NASA to join the first manned mission to Mars.

100001495.title: Eight Below
100001495.description: Stranded in Antarctica due to an unforgiving winter storm, a team of sled dogs must survive together until their determined trainer can rescue them.

100001591.title: Space Jam: A New Legacy
100001591.description: When a rogue artificial intelligence kidnaps his son, LeBron James recruits the Looney Tunes to face off against the Goons in a game of basketball.

100001592.title: Tom & Jerry: The Movie
100001592.description: A desperate event planner conspires with Tom to catch his nemesis Jerry as the mouse wreaks havoc throughout a fancy Manhattan hotel during a wedding.

100001596.title: Mortal Kombat
100001596.description: An MMA fighter with a mysterious dragon birthmark learns that he’s been chosen to fight for Earthrealm in the final battle against the evil Outworld.

100001602.title: Godzilla
100001602.description: A mysterious creature causes a meltdown at a nuclear power plant. Years later, the monster goes on a rampage that can only be stopped by Godzilla.

100001741.title: Nerve
100001741.description: A high school senior finds herself immersed in an online game of truth or dare, where her every move becomes manipulated by a community of "watchers."

100001746.title: 10 Rules for Sleeping Around
100001746.description: An engaged couple seeking advice from happily married friends learns the secret to marital longevity is an open relationship dictated by ten rules.

100001904.title: Rescue the Earth
100001904.description: The human race’s only chance at fighting against the alien giant that annihilated planet Earth is in the hands of a young boy. Can he save humanity?

100001910.title: Forgiving God
100001910.description: Arriving at his final foster home after growing up in the system, Jon meets a girl in the woods who teaches him about faith and forgiveness.

100001931.title: Wheels of Terror
100001931.description: The story of the 27th Panzers, a German combat regiment composed of prisoners who are sent on a doomed mission to destroy a Soviet train during WWII.

100002070.title: Bad Cat
100002070.description: A profane house cat must deal with the arrival of his illegitimate son, an accidental killing, his owner's eviction and more within the course of a day of debauchery and mayhem.

100002108.title: The Killer
100002108.description: A retired hitman finds himself on a rescue mission when the 17-year-old girl he's agreed to look after gets in trouble with shady people.

100002154.title: Damaged Goods
100002154.description: Since he was born, life hasn’t been easy for Chosen. Fending for himself, he quickly learns how to survive on the cold streets of Detroit.

100002159.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
100002159.description: The Bride continues her quest for revenge, fighting her way through a host of assassins in pursuit of a final showdown with the man who betrayed her.

100002172.title: Creature From Black Lake
100002172.description: Two graduate students travel to the Louisiana swamps in the hopes of documenting a Bigfoot-like creature that is terrorizing the local fishermen.

100002202.title: Unforgivable
100002202.description: After abusing his family and nearly killing his girlfriend, a man is ordered to either participate in an innovative therapy program or go to jail.

100002544.title: The Perfect Student
100002544.description: A well-respected criminology professor becomes a target herself when she tries to establish the innocence of her star student in a murder case.

100002596.title: Keyholes Are for Peeping
100002596.description: In this funny parody of adult films, a momma’s boy gets a marriage counseling certificate and starts giving marital advice to couples in his building.

0300010105.title: One Day at a Time
0300010105.description: This situation comedy revolves around a single mother trying to be an understanding parent to her two headstrong teenage daughters.

02044.title: Flavor of Love
02044.description: 20 different women line up to date rapper Flavor Flav and win his heart, but first they must compete for quality time by taking on various challenges.

0300008051.description: Regina King, Marla Gibbs, and Jackée Harry are comedy gold in this family sitcom about life in a middle-class apartment building in Washington, D.C.

0300010317.title: Southern Fried Homicide
0300010317.description: Serving up salacious true crime stories from south of the Mason-Dixon Line, this series shows the evil that can lurk behind Southern hospitality.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

0300008835.title: Sanctuary
0300008835.description: As gene therapy, transplants and cloning offer hope for humanity, a dark side of evolution produces monsters a select few are brave enough to take on.

0300004999.title: Garfield and Friends
0300004999.description: Lazy, lasagna-loving cat Garfield has fun adventures with his pal Odie and owner Jon.

0300007226.title: Behind Bars: The World's Toughest Prisons
0300007226.description: Imagine prisons so tough that even the hardest gang bosses and killers learn the meaning of fear. This extraordinary series is an intimate portrait of crime and punishment that goes beyond the gates, walls, barred windows and cells of the world's toughest maximum security prisons. From Bolivia to Bulgaria, Dallas to Arizona, enter a world of hardened criminals and prisoners that few ever glimpse.

0300005165.title: Divorce Court
0300005165.description: Judge Star Jones is the new face of Divorce Court presiding with her wisdom & experience. Join this new era through tears, laughter, truth & realness!

0300000087.title: Deputy
0300000087.description: When an elected sheriff dies, an arcane rule in the county charter, forged back in the Wild West, suddenly thrusts the most unlikely man into the job.

0300010091.title: Kitchen Commando
0300010091.description: Chef Andre Rush brings the might of the military to restaurants across America as he takes up the mission to save the struggling service industry.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

0300000121.title: Hawthorne
0300000121.description: A recently-widowed nursing director and mother struggles to hold the middle ground between bureaucratic administrators and apathetic colleagues.

0300010053.title: Fantasy Island (2021 Series)
0300010053.description: This modern drama series takes place at a luxury resort, where any fantasy requested by guests is fulfilled—although they rarely turn out as expected.

03321.title: Kitchen Nightmares
03321.description: World-famous chef Gordon Ramsay gives struggling restaurants across the United States a week of his time, advice, and a fighting chance to succeed.

0300009557.title: El Mariachi
0300009557.description: A través de una serie de circunstancias desafortunadas, un músico de mariachi descubre que lo buscan por un asesinato que no cometió.

0300010306.title: Long Lost Family
0300010306.description: In this engaging reality series, hosts Chris Jacobs and Lisa Joyner help people reunite with long lost family members and loved ones.

0300006557.title: No Easy Days
0300006557.description: After the U.S. President’s daughter is kidnapped, he'll have to enlist a rebellious Navy SEAL—and face his own shortcomings—to get her back.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

0300010240.title: Tremors: The Series
0300010240.description: In the sleepy desert town of Perfection, Nevada, a no-nonsense survivalist struggles to maintain an uneasy peace with a giant prehistoric albino worm.

0300000074.title: Alaska Monsters
0300000074.description: A team of outdoorsmen hunt for cryptic creatures in the Alaska Triangle, a treacherous 200,000-mile region known for unusual disappearances.

0300000159.title: Hannibal
0300000159.description: An FBI investigator with the ability to empathize with psychopaths is assigned to work with renowned psychiatrist—and secret cannibal—Hannibal Lecter.

0300008958.title: Bonanza
actors: Lorne Greene Pernell Roberts Dan Blocker Michael Landon Guy Williams
0300008958.description: On their 1,000-square mile Ponderosa Ranch in late-1850’s Nevada, Ben Cartwright and his three sons defend their land, business and fellow citizenry.

03320.title: Hell's Kitchen
03320.description: Renowned restauranteur Gordon Ramsay hosts a fierce competition for aspiring chefs, as they vie for a prestigious job at one of his eateries.

0300010209.title: Spenser: For Hire
0300010209.description: Renaissance man Spenser cruises the streets in a vintage Mustang, solving cases for those who prefer a touch of class in their private investigators.

0300008574.title: Malcolm & Eddie
0300008574.description: A mid-1990’s odd couple story revolving around a carefree slob and tow truck operator and his preppy, neatfreak, aspiring sportscaster roommate.

0300006874.title: The Nanny
0300006874.description: Fran Drescher stars as a jilted bride from Flushing, Queens who talks her way into becoming a nanny for a wealthy widower’s dysfunctional children.

0300007764.title: Pokémon the Series: Black & White
0300007764.description: Ash and Pikachu are off to the distant Unova region, where they'll encounter new friends, new rivals, new challenges, and all-new Pokémon! Upon arrival, Ash meets aspiring Dragon Master Iris, full of spirit and determination, and Pokémon Connoisseur Cilan, who is always available to lend his expertise. Above all, Ash will need plenty of new Pokémon on his team if he wants to win Unova's tournaments and Gym badges. Following his every move is the criminal trio of Team Rocket, with sinister new schemes and a fresh resolve to catch Pikachu! Then there's the mysterious N...is he a friend or a foe, and what is his connection with the secret organization known as Team Plasma? And what is Team Plasma planning to do with one of the Legendary Pokémon of the Unova region? Once this adventure starts, the excitement won't stop!

0300009126.title: Unsung
0300009126.description: A documentary series that profiles some of the most influential, talented yet forgotten R&B, Soul and Gospel artists of the 1970s, '80s and '90s.

0300007907.title: Brickleberry
0300007907.description: Daniel Tosh stars as the lead voice in this Comedy Central cartoon series about a group of national park rangers who are terrible at their jobs.
